 periods.<br><br>IMHO Sony/VI/989 all did a fairly decent job of correcting problems as they were found.  Not an awesome job but a good job.<br><br>Kothall Landrunner<br>62nd Level Druid</p>&nbsp;<br></td></td></tr>
